               <p>33. <rs id="t17751206-25-deflabel105" type="occupation">Captain</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17751206-25-defend547 t17751206-25-deflabel105"></join> ROCHE, on Saturday the 8th of December, was brought to the bar, to be tried on a special commission, for the murder of Captain 
               <persName id="t17751206-25-person545">
                  David
                   Fergusson
               <interp inst="t17751206-25-person545" type="surname" value="Fergusson"></interp>
